<h1 class="h1costume" >Costum made</h1>
<section class="grid_1-1">
    
    <p class="costumep" >At Solrig Design, everything is about you and your unique style. We offer custom-made designs that are created exactly according to your wishes. Whether you dream of a lively color palette, a certain style, or a detail that makes the product really special, we can make it come true.</p>
    <img class="costumeimg1" src="./gallery/costume1.png" alt="costume" width="325px">
        
    </section>

    <section class="grid_1-2" >
        <img class="costumeimg2" src="./gallery/costume2.png" alt="costume">
        <p class="costumepp">
            Put together your style: 1. You choose the product's design, colors and any details such as patterns, materials or personal additions (e.g. initials or special symbols).
            How to order: 2. When you have designed your product, you put it in the basket and complete your order.
            Production time: 3. As your product is custom made, it takes up to 2 weeks to produce from the moment we receive your order. We make sure to keep you updated so you always know how far we are in the process.</p>
            
    </section>

    <h1 class="faq" >Frequently asked questions</h1>

    <style>
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid_1-1 {
    gap: 50px;
